## `test_rmdir_on_root_raises(as_root)`
<!-- checksum: placeholder-nodes-10 -->

### Purpose
The root directory cannot be removed. Attempting to do so is a permission-class error per the project's idea.md rule "root directory is automatically created by mkfs; rmdir('/') is always PermissionError."

### Postconditions

```python
with pytest.raises(PermissionDenied):
    as_root.rmdir("/")
```

